  "texts": [
    "Improving upon DICP, Wu et al. [149].",
    "and Yoon et al. [158] integrate the Doppler velocity factor in a continuous-time odometry framework.",
    "These works suggest that the degeneracy problem can be effectively addressed through the use of FMCW LiDAR.",
    "Degraded environmentA degraded environment is one that presents challenges to the sensing ability of LiDAR, unlike a degenerative environment.",
    "LiDAR operates by emitting a laser pulse and detecting its return after interacting with objects, and this process can be disrupted by unwanted particles obstructing the pulse's path."
  ]
}